    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  Several French regions where COVID19 has been reported currently show a renewed increase in ILI cases in the general practice based\n                  <jats:italic>Sentinelles</jats:italic>\n                  network. Here we computed the number of excess cases by region and found correlation with the number of reported COVID19 cases so far. These data suggest larger circulation of SARS-CoV-2 in the French population than apparent from confirmed cases.\n                </jats:p>",
